  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: General Pharmaceutical Council Register - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_pharmaceutical_council_register">General Pharmaceutical Council Register</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_register">REGISTER</xref>
 maintained by the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_pharmaceutical_council">General Pharmaceutical Council</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_pharmaceutical_council_register">General Pharmaceutical Council Register</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_pharmaceutical_council_register">GPhC Register</xref>) is divided into three parts:        </p>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_pharmacist">Pharmacists</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_pharmacy_technician">Pharmacy Technicians</xref>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_pharmacy_premises">Pharmacy Premises</xref>
               <p>.</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_general_pharmaceutical_council_register">General Pharmaceutical Council Register</xref>, see the 
              <xref href="https://www.pharmacyregulation.org/"
               scope="external"
               format="html">General Pharmaceutical Council website</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
